{
  "stem": "21786.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] This is not just some presents which were given-- and mentioned that it coincides with Hanukkah.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And there was a menorah in my grandfather's house, but that was about all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But it was always something which coincides with the goyish or the Aryan type of surrounding.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I went to the synagogue with my father and with my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And it was already so progressive that there were men and women together, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which probably, for that time, was very reformed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The rabbi was a very nice guy, a very nice man with a beard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he was very kind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I had a bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I was prepared for it by, I forgot the name of the melamed who taught me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I learned it by heart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I didn't know what I am saying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "A prayer so similar, my grandfather invoked prayers, especially in the village, which was in the mountains, and that was a storm coming.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And there were the lightnings coming down, and simply there was the thunder.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And everything was trembling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Suddenly, there was a Bible on the table.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And my grandfather was praying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "So I connected always the prayer to some kind of a fear-- why one prays.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I remember that the bar mitzvah-- we had at home some kind of a family reunion.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "My relatives and some friends, I don't know how many people were there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But it was done at home, simply at a dining room table, and the rabbi was there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "In school, religion was taught as a subject.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It was either a Roman Catholic religion, or the Protestant.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Or the Jews, they had their religion classes were fused.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Usually in the afternoon, one hour or two hours in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
